_tasks_complete suite | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4925→| **P3** | Clean up legacy `black.box` references | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4926→| **P3** | Clean up `1-1-foo` phantom story ($24.35) | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4927→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_016W9JK5jpLzQYWdbCzNmHNq","session_id":"72102346-2cce-494f-a433-46e61afe630e","uuid":"248be444-defe-47c5-ae20-721271f8cd22","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:46:16.152Z"}
